  - `sweep_expired(pool, now: DateTime<Utc>) -> u64` — `UPDATE billing_checkouts SET status='expired', expired_at=$1, updated_at=$1 WHERE status='pending' AND expires_at < $1` (uses the existing partial index). Returns rows affected.
