## §7 Handoff to M5 — credit spending integration

M5 is the debit side + the spending guardrail (Q9: A1 + B2 + C2).

- `atelier-payments/src/guard.rs` (new) — `reserve_or_402(pool, user_id, kind, amount, reason, ref_id) -> Result<(), GuardError>`: one tx, read balance via `balances_for_user`; `balance < amount` ⇒ `Insufficient`; else `insert_debit` (`delta = -amount`).
