- Hawkes-fit dispatch — same with `CreditKind::Compute, HAWKES_FIT_COST`.
- Cost constants (`HAWKES_FIT_COST`, `TASK_RUN_COST`) — land wherever spending lives (a small `costs.rs`); no SKU catalog needed.
